OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782227911
OL,3,CThousands of unsafe toys seized at
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FThousands of unsafe toys were seized
OL,7,Fduring this year's Appleby Horse Fair,
OL,8,Ftrading standards officers have
OL,9,Frevealed.
OL,11,FTwo days of targeted enforcement
OL,12,Foperations were carried out during the
OL,13,Fevent by Westmorland and Furness
OL,14,FCouncil's Trading Standards team,
OL,15,Falongside Cumbria Police and Anti-
OL,16,FCounterfeiting Group representatives.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
