PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782227911
OL,3,CThousands of unsafe toys seized at
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FDuring this operation, officers
OL,7,Finspected eight stalls and confiscated
OL,8,F"squishy cheese and butter block"
OL,9,Ffidget toys. These toys are soft foam
OL,10,Fproducts, which slowly rise after
OL,11,Fbeing squished.
OL,13,FOther toys seized were what the
OL,14,Fcouncil described as "potentially
OL,15,Fdangerous counterfeit versions of
OL,16,Fviral toys," like squishy bun
OL,17,Fdumplings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782227911
OL,3,CThousands of unsafe toys seized at
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FAll of the seized items either lacked
OL,7,Fsafety labels, or were confirmed as
OL,8,Fcounterfeit. As such, it is unlikely
OL,9,Fthey had undergone safety testing or
OL,10,Fmeet legal standards.
OL,12,FThe Trading Standards team advise
OL,13,Fparents and carers to buy only from
OL,14,Freputable retailers or approved
OL,15,Fresellers, and to check for proper
OL,16,Fsafety markings like the UKCA or CE
OL,17,Fmarks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
