PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782227911
OL,3,CThousands of unsafe toys seized at
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FCatherine Hornby, Westmorland and
OL,7,FFurness Council Trading Standards
OL,8,FManager, said: "We will not hesitate
OL,9,Fto take action where traders put
OL,10,Fconsumers at risk. Products designed
OL,11,Ffor children must meet strict safety
OL,12,Frequirements, and we will continue to
OL,13,Fcarry out enforcement activity to
OL,14,Fremove unsafe items from the market."
OL,16,FPolice Gold Commander for Appleby
OL,17,FHorse Fair 2026, Detective
OL,18,FSuperintendent Dan St Quintin, said,
OL,19,F"Police and Trading Standards worked
OL,20,Fclosely together during this year's
OL,21,FFair.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
